rComments: He is a great Prof, enough said. He did scare me the first lecture on plagiarism, but that is to be expected. Other than that, he did care and knew how to teach. If you ever come back to UTSC Sergi, I will sign up immediately!
Great Prof! Took many courses with him and got great grades!
Great prof and easy class if you show up and try hard!
Funny and easily explains something if you don't understand, both in class and in his office hours.  I've taken several courses he's taught and I've loved them all
Prof. Lopez-Torres was my favourite prof last term! I will take any course he teaches!!!

I had Prof. Lopez-Torres for my first science class ever in university, and he is honestly an amazing professor! His lecture slides were easy to understand, and his lecturing was simple and clear. He made the material being taught so interesting and easy to grasp. He is so kind and understanding, and I would recommend taking his class any day!
